<paragraph id="8BDA36EF9406FFDCBA9F3B4CFCDAFD92" blockId="9.[151,1437,326,2008]" pageId="9" pageNumber="260">
<emphasis id="B911EAFD9406FFDCBA9F3B4CFF7DFECA" bold="true" box="[151,224,326,352]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="260">Types.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFF44B1E9406FFDCBAE03B4CFE0BFECB" author="Suffrian, E." box="[232,406,326,353]" pageId="9" pageNumber="260" pagination="1 - 483" refId="ref25218" refString="Suffrian, E. (1866) Zur Kenntnis der Sudamerikanischen Cryptocephalen. Linnaea Entomologica, 16, 1 - 483." type="journal article" year="1866">Suffrian (1866)</bibRefCitation>
did not mention the number of specimens under study but stated that no males were available for the study. He reported a generic “ 
<collectingCountry id="F372767F9406FFDCB87F3B60FD6DFE2E" box="[631,752,362,388]" name="Venezuela" pageId="9" pageNumber="260">Venezuela</collectingCountry>
” as provenance of the species, a single collector (“Moritz”) and a single depository: NMV (“Mus. Vindob.”). A single specimen was found in NMV. The specimen bears a label that appears to be quite recently added. A 
<typeStatus id="54DE884D9406FFDCB8653BB8FD49FE66" box="[621,724,434,460]" pageId="9" pageNumber="260">lectotype</typeStatus>
is designated as follows: 
<typeStatus id="54DE884D9406FFDCB9FD3BB8FBC1FE66" box="[1013,1116,434,460]" pageId="9" pageNumber="260">lectotype</typeStatus>
(by present designation): 
<specimenCount id="9D63FD669406FFDCBF883BB8FA0AFE66" box="[1408,1431,434,460]" pageId="9" pageNumber="260" type="male">♂</specimenCount>
, glued, aedeagus extracted and glued, together with the abdomen, on the same label bearing the specimen, // “Dr Moritz 1858 
<collectingCountry id="F372767F9406FFDCBB263BF0FE39FDBE" box="[302,420,506,532]" name="Venezuela" pageId="9" pageNumber="260">Venezuela</collectingCountry>
” [white label, printed] // “54” [white label, printed] // “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C654D6C9406FFDCBE213BF0FF52FD92" authority="Suffrian, 1866" authorityName=", Suffrian" authorityYear="1866" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Metallactus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="260" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="latiusculus">
<emphasis id="B911EAFD9406FFDCBE213BF0FAADFDBE" box="[1065,1328,506,532]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="260">Metallactus latiusculus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFF44B1E9406FFDCBF323BF0FF52FD92" author="Suffrian, E." pageId="9" pageNumber="260" pagination="1 - 483" refId="ref25218" refString="Suffrian, E. (1866) Zur Kenntnis der Sudamerikanischen Cryptocephalen. Linnaea Entomologica, 16, 1 - 483." type="journal article" year="1866">Suffrian, 1866</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
<subScript id="17E134AA9406FFDCBADE382FFECEFD9C" attach="right" box="[214,339,549,566]" fontSize="7" pageId="9" pageNumber="260">
<typeStatus id="54DE884D9406FFDCBADE382FFECEFD9C" box="[214,339,549,566]" pageId="9" pageNumber="260">LECTOTYPUS</typeStatus>
</subScript>
D. Sassi des.” [red label, printed] // (NMV).
</paragraph>
